node.text:
Using Lightroom mobile app to edit up 8 photos from Amalfi last summer, I edited using my presets from @doyoutravelpresets that are included in The Preset Bundle.
I used to take sooo long to edit each image & now I can edit soo quickly, a fun way I explained presets to a friend was that they are a creators years of experience & practice packaged into a 1 step editing process ☺️
Link to the Preset Bundle https://www.thepresetbundle.com/?ref=gypsealust

node.title: Editing 8 pictures in 10 minutes- Tips & Tricks!

node.text:
I’d be lying if I didn’t admit I often use self tan, I recently tried out @minetanbodyskin & I must say it gives such a natural result, no one would ever know I was using one! 
It gives a salon quality tan, from home! It’s also Vegan and Cruelty Free 🐰 using 100% natural DHA! 

They have a Q&A on their site to find which product & shade is most suitable for you which I thought was really unique! I’m using their intensely hydrating ‘Coconut Water Self Tan Foam’ and I only leave it for 1-2 hours to get a subtle, natural but deep tan 💗

Use ‘LAUREN25’ for 25% off! #MineTan #MineTanResults

node.text:
Fulfilling my lavender field dreams 💜 & it even smelt better than it looks 😛

They are currently blooming now across Provence 😍
Merci for everyone sending recommendations on the best ones to visit!

To get to this exact spot put Lavandes Angelvin into google maps & head there for sunset, it’s so beautiful 💜💜

#France #Provence #Valensole #Lavenderfield
